version_description: The version 2 that's out there is almost perfect except I think it mistakenly uses some different chords during the chorus. Also, there is an amazing BBC video of him doing this song. The tab is actually the album version, but I lifted his chord shapes from the BBC video. Frankly, the other versions beyond 2 are just incorrect chord-wise from what I can tell.
Full chords for easy auto-scroll / intermediate version with maj7, sus and split chords / indications of breaks.
There wasn't a tab yet on the site. It's adapted for guitar from the honky-tonk like piano he plays on the record. During the instrumental you can whistle or play the harmonica like Neil does.
